<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Power of Attorney</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #1f2937;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 48px 40px;
            background: white;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding-bottom: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 36px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }

        .doc-title {
            font-size: 30px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #111827;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.06em;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .doc-subtitle {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #6b7280;
        }

        .stamp-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 6px 16px;
            border-radius: 9999px;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            background: #ecfdf5;
            color: #059669;
            margin-top: 12px;
        }

        .parties-section {
            margin: 28px 0;
        }

        .party-card {
            background: #f9fafb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .party-label {
            font-size: 11px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.06em;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .party-name {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .party-details {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #4b5563;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .content {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #374151;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .content p {
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .clause {
            margin: 20px 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background: #f9fafb;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .clause h4 {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .clause p {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #4b5563;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .clause ul {
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        .clause li {
            margin-bottom: 6px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #4b5563;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .powers-list {
            background: #eff6ff;
            border: 1px solid #bfdbfe;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .powers-list h4 {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1e40af;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        }

        .powers-list ul {
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        .powers-list li {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #1e3a5f;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .important-box {
            background: #fef2f2;
            border: 1px solid #fecaca;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 24px 0;
        }

        .important-box h4 {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #991b1b;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .important-box p {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #7f1d1d;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .signature-section {
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        .sig-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 32px;
        }

        .sig-card {
            background: #f9fafb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 24px;
        }

        .sig-title {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .sig-field {
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .sig-field-label {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6b7280;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .sig-field-line {
            border-bottom: 1px solid #d1d5db;
            height: 24px;
        }

        .witness-section {
            margin-top: 32px;
            background: #f9fafb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 24px;
        }

        .witness-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 24px;
            margin-top: 16px;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 48px;
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 24px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            color: #9ca3af;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="header">
        <div class="doc-title">Power of Attorney</div>
        <div class="doc-subtitle">General / Special Power of Attorney</div>
        <div class="stamp-badge">Non-Judicial Stamp Paper — ₹100</div>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <p>KNOW ALL MEN BY THESE PRESENTS that I/We, the undersigned, do hereby constitute, nominate, and appoint the
            person named herein as my/our lawful Attorney to act on my/our behalf.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="parties-section">
        <div class="party-card">
            <div class="party-label">Principal (Grantor)</div>
            <div class="party-name">{{principalName}}</div>
            <div class="party-details">
                {{{principalAddress}}}
                {{#if principalIdType}}<br><strong>ID:</strong> {{principalIdType}} — {{principalIdNumber}}{{/if}}
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="party-card">
            <div class="party-label">Attorney (Agent)</div>
            <div class="party-name">{{attorneyName}}</div>
            <div class="party-details">
                {{{attorneyAddress}}}
                {{#if attorneyIdType}}<br><strong>ID:</strong> {{attorneyIdType}} — {{attorneyIdNumber}}{{/if}}
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <div class="powers-list">
            <h4>Powers Granted</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>To execute, sign, and deliver any and all documents, agreements, contracts, deeds, and instruments
                    on behalf of the Principal.</li>
                <li>To appear before any government authority, court, tribunal, or regulatory body and represent the
                    Principal in all matters.</li>
                <li>To open, operate, and close bank accounts; sign cheques, demand drafts, and authorize fund
                    transfers.</li>
                <li>To purchase, sell, lease, mortgage, or otherwise deal with immovable and movable property belonging
                    to the Principal.</li>
                <li>To institute or defend any legal proceedings, suits, claims, or appeals on behalf of the Principal.
                </li>
                {{#if additionalPowers}}<li>{{{additionalPowers}}}</li>{{/if}}
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <h4>Duration and Validity</h4>
            <p>This Power of Attorney shall remain in full force and effect from <strong>{{effectiveDate}}</strong>
                {{#if expiryDate}}until <strong>{{expiryDate}}</strong>{{else}}until expressly revoked in writing by the
                Principal{{/if}}. The Principal retains the right to revoke this Power of Attorney at any time by
                providing written notice to the Attorney.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <h4>Scope and Limitations</h4>
            <p>{{{purposeDescription}}}</p>
            <p>The Attorney shall act in good faith and in the best interests of the Principal at all times. The
                Attorney shall not delegate powers granted herein unless expressly authorized. All acts performed by the
                Attorney within the scope of this Power of Attorney shall be deemed as acts of the Principal.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="important-box">
            <h4>Legal Declaration</h4>
            <p>I/We hereby ratify and confirm all acts lawfully done by the said Attorney pursuant to this Power of
                Attorney. I/We declare that this Power of Attorney is given freely and voluntarily, without any
                coercion, undue influence, or misrepresentation.</p>
        </div>

        <p><strong>IN WITNESS WHEREOF,</strong> I/We have executed this Power of Attorney on this
            <strong>{{effectiveDate}}</strong> at {{#if executionPlace}}{{executionPlace}}{{else}}the place mentioned
            above{{/if}}.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="signature-section">
        <div class="sig-grid">
            <div class="sig-card">
                <div class="sig-title">Principal (Grantor)</div>
                <div class="sig-field">
                    <div class="sig-field-label">Signature</div>
                    <div class="sig-field-line"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="sig-field">
                    <div class="sig-field-label">Name: {{principalName}}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="sig-field">
                    <div class="sig-field-label">Date</div>
                    <div class="sig-field-line"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="sig-card">
                <div class="sig-title">Attorney (Agent)</div>
                <div class="sig-field">
                    <div class="sig-field-label">Acceptance Signature</div>
                    <div class="sig-field-line"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="sig-field">
                    <div class="sig-field-label">Name: {{attorneyName}}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="sig-field">
                    <div class="sig-field-label">Date</div>
                    <div class="sig-field-line"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="witness-section">
            <div class="sig-title">Witnesses</div>
            <div class="witness-grid">
                <div>
                    <div class="sig-field">
                        <div class="sig-field-label">Witness 1 — Signature</div>
                        <div class="sig-field-line"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="sig-field">
                        <div class="sig-field-label">Name & Address</div>
                        <div class="sig-field-line"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <div class="sig-field">
                        <div class="sig-field-label">Witness 2 — Signature</div>
                        <div class="sig-field-line"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="sig-field">
                        <div class="sig-field-label">Name & Address</div>
                        <div class="sig-field-line"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>This Power of Attorney is executed on non-judicial stamp paper of appropriate value.</p>
        <p>Legal Document System</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>